# Placeholder for Keycloak realm exports.

# A `vulis-realm-dev.json` export will be added in M1.2 with:
#   - a `vulis` realm
#   - default roles: admin, data-scientist, annotator, operator, reviewer
#   - one dev user per role (password = role name, e.g. admin/admin)
#   - OIDC clients for: web app, tauri app, gateway
#
# To generate the initial realm, you can use the Keycloak admin UI on a
# running dev stack, then export with:
#
#   docker exec -it <keycloak-container> \
#     /opt/keycloak/bin/kc.sh export \
#       --realm vulis --dir /opt/keycloak/data/import --users realm_file
